<ab facs="#facs_44_r1l5">hat von VVernher Neẅmeırs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc . das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_44_r1l6">wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> vormals ʒu </ab>
